{
  "stem": "26609.17",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She went before me, younger sister, who is now in France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She survived too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And she was not far from me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We didn't-- each other didn't know about ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We didn't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I-- I didn't believe that she was alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I believed, rather, that my brother-- I loved him dearly, my brother, eldest brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] never found him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, dates, we never thought of dates there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who would-- if I would sometimes write a day, or write a letter, or think, we didn't live a normal life to remember.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I often didn't remember it was Monday or Sunday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't-- that was not a life that-- that-- in a normal life, you have to think of a date, of a month, a year.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You write a-- you write here, you write there, write a check-- we didn't need it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just lived from day to day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know, often, if it's-- I got up in the morning, if it's night or morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we walked, we walked to [INAUDIBLE], yes?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And where-- I think straight away, we left, as soon as we heard that the war was over, although it wasn't over there, not everywhere, but slowly, slowly.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In [NON-ENGLISH], they searched for [INAUDIBLE], as I said, and-- to register with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because I wanted to go back, and there was not normal transport, no transport, no way to go back to Poland to search for relatives of survivors.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I thought maybe if I joined the Red Cross, through them maybe I can go back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no-- no train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nothing was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People didn't travel just after the war, or during the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
